						               													<description>Welcome to the ghost competition at the old turret clock! As they do every night, the ghosts are coming together to play their fun game on the clock. When the clock strikes midnight, the clock arm will start moving. Left, right, left, right, there's something wrong with the clock! The players need to place their ghosts on the wicked clock, but the clock arm will try to swipe the ghosts off the clock. Once the arm stops, the round is over and each player counts, how many of his ghosts could hang on to the clock. Whoever has the most, wins the round and gets to place one of the ghosts on to the winner podium. The first player to win three rounds will be the new champion - but only for one day, when the challenge will start again!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
